  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>This hotel is great for leisure and business travelers. There is also rooftop pool with Jacuzzi, sauna, steam-room and fitness center. (07/06SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located in the mid of central city area on Sukhumvit Soi 19. Just only 2 minutes from Robinson Department Store, very convenience for traveling around Bangkok since easy access to both sky train, Asoke station and subway Sukhumvit station. It is just only 30 minutes to Suvarnabhumi Airport.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>There are 76 one-bedroom suites with fully kitchenette equipment.  Rooms are very large in size with balcony.  Deluxe Suite is 71-80 square meters. Executive Suite is 96 Square meters. Separated bedroom and living area. All the rooms are modern decorated with modern furniture and wooden floor. Each room provides 2 flat screen color TV, washing machine, DVD player and high speed Internet.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is a high-rise building, constructed with concrete and glass in yellow color.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>Mediterranean restaurant and wine bar located on the ground floor next to the lobby area serving all day dinning.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>Lobby is a medium size with limited black sofa seats. Modern decoration. Free Internet access in Lobby area.</Text>
